    "text": "Cyber Vulnerability Disclosure Reporting Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to submit a report describing the policies and procedures developed to coordinate the disclosure of cyber vulnerabilities. The report shall describe instances\u00a0when these policies and procedures were used to disclose cyber vulnerabilities in the previous year. Further, the report shall\u00a0mention the degree to which the disclosed information was acted upon by stakeholders."
